		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Use the debug book 6. Set Quest flags and options &gt; 6. Act 3 (LOW) &gt; 23. Fireworks House &gt; 1. Knows password. &#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Teleport to 13, 16, -127 in CTY_Main_A. Go in to twahe shop and talk to the guard on your right, use the password so he unlocks  the Vault door behind him. Go through the door and up the stairs. Try and go behind the counter at the top of the stairs and the warning will trigger." />
